@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultTextAlignment left
skinparam ArrowColor #1F2937
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #DCFCE7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #16A34A
skinparam rectangle {
  FontColor #111827
  BorderColor #1F2937
}

title Auth Client After: Email List Fallback + Strict Admin Revoke Contract

rectangle "createClient().auth.user.email.list()" as UserEmail #DBEAFE
rectangle "Primary route" as PrimaryRoute #D1FAE5
rectangle "Legacy fallback route" as LegacyRoute #E0E7FF

UserEmail --> PrimaryRoute : GET /email/list
PrimaryRoute --> LegacyRoute : fallback only on HTTP 404\nGET /email-list

note right of UserEmail
Modern route first for server v1.6.0+.
Compatibility fallback keeps older installs working.
end note

rectangle "createClient().auth.admin.user.session.revoke(input)" as Revoke #D1FAE5
rectangle "Validation gate" as Gate #BBF7D0
rectangle "/admin/revoke-user-session" as Single #E5E7EB
rectangle "/admin/revoke-user-sessions" as Plural #E5E7EB

Revoke --> Gate : normalize payload
Gate --> Single : single payload -> POST { userId, sessionToken }
Gate --> Plural : plural payload -> POST { userId }

note right of Gate
Requires non-empty userId.
Plural inputs must share one userId.
Mixed-user lists are rejected client-side.
end note
@enduml
